{
  "stem": "12150.3",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "It was not civilian construction.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "It was-- I believe, it was construction for the army, army buildings.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But there was no food, no extra food.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And it was hard work, and it was no good.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "So I, I kept switching kommandos.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And then, one day, I was assigned to a kommando that was digging ditches somewhere in fields, but there was food in the fields.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "It was turnips.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And we could-- actually, we could eat while we were working-- raw turnips, but it's life sustaining.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And of course, we couldn't do it while the SS guards.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Once in a while, you had SS guards, they didn't care.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "They didn't care.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "They turned the other way, but that was rare.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Usually, they'd beat us if they found it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "They didn't shoot us for that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "You take a turnip form the field, you ate it, it's OK.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And in the same area we were digging ditches-- I don't remember why these ditches or what-- or what the purpose of the ditches were.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And there was groups of girls walking by.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And these girls worked in the offices or whatever.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And they dropped bread into the ditches.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "On the way, they dropped bread in the ditches as they walked by.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "So that helped.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And this was going on for a while and [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] until November, I believe, or so.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And then it got very cold and once in a while, I stayed off as sick.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "I stayed home as sick and hoped that they won't catch me.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was It was.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was dangerous because once in a while-- they didn't come every day with trucks.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Occasionally, they rounded up the, the sick and the disabled and so on.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
